ce management systems, and video management software. It offers its products to government establishments, retail chains, financial institutions, residential, industrial warehouse, public spaces, and infrastructure projects. The company was formerly known as Perfect Lucky Goldstar International Limited and changed its name to Aditya Infotech Limited in August 1997. The company was founded in 1994 and is based in Noida, India.", "fullTimeEmployees": 1274, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Hari Shanker Khemka", "age": 72, "title": "Chairman & Whole-Time Director", "yearBorn": 1953, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Aditya  Khemka", "age": 51, "title": "MD & Director", "yearBorn": 1974, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Yogesh Chand Sharma", "age": 58, "title": "Chief Financial Officer", "yearBorn": 1967, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Roshni  Tandon", "title": "Company Secretary & Compliance Officer", "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Ananmay  Khemka", "age": 26, "title": "Whole-Time Director", "yearBorn": 1999, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Sanjay  Gogia", "age": 55, "title": "President of Sales", "yearBorn": 1970, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Anup  Nair", "age": 47, "title": "President of Strategy & Business Development", "yearBorn": 1978, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Monika  Sharma", "title": "Senior Vice President of Research & Development and Product Development", "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}], "executiveTeam": [], "maxAge": 86400, "priceHint": 2, "previousClose": 1674.5, "open": 1700.0, "dayLow": 1683.7, "dayHigh": 1740.1, "regularMarketPreviousClose": 1674.5, "regularMarketOpen": 1700.0, "regularMarketDayLow": 1683.7, "regularMarketDayHigh": 1740.1, "payou